    <item>
      <title>中国14年来最严重的通货紧缩给央行带来压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/china-consumer-prices-drop-for-third-month-on-weak-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的消费者价格出现自2009年以来最长的连续下跌趋势，可能会出现通缩螺旋，可能需要更多的政府支持才能扭转。其出口增长引擎也步履蹒跚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/china-consumer-prices-drop-for-third-month-on-weak-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 01:34:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国空袭胡塞武装助长中东紧张局势，油价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国及其盟国对也门胡塞叛军发动空袭，加大对红海船只袭击的报复力度，这些袭击危及了通过重要水道的燃料和货物流动，油价大幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 23:02:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
